{
  "stem": "25938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes we used to take the handkerchiefs and like make-- make, like we wipe our noses to show that we are-- we are active, that we are here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I used to tell them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- I was the leader of this group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he recognized me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't recognize him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- I think he was from Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can't forgive myself for not taking his telephone number.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was the only one to-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have the phlegm comes up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was I remember from that-- from this-- working in the underground.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was in the packages, I never opened it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have to have meetings too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to have meetings too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know, I say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the rest I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I, see--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All these 25 people, we were just-- were marching to a certain place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working, making [? people ?] believe we are struggling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I just saw him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't even remember their names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was in contact with these three people, Shayek Urlich, whom I gave this package.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Regina Kuperberg, and the man-- the man who introduced me to that group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wonder.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, I wonder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that you know of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think-- [INAUDIBLE] Shayek Urlich, I think, was in Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think-- [INAUDIBLE], I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few times they did-- they brought me even food later when I used to work before that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shayek Urlich.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was work against the-- against the-- against the SS, against the-- against the--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a few people escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was known, known in the literature.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some-- some made it and some didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
